      <title>警惕的亚洲官员试图确保特朗普关税缓刑棒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/wary-asian-officials-seek-to-ensure-trump-tariff-reprieve-sticks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲的官员对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的90天停顿对数十个贸易伙伴的关税持续了90天，并以救济，谨慎和一点嘲笑的混合方式做出了反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/wary-asian-officials-seek-to-ensure-trump-tariff-reprieve-sticks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 02:52:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自关税缓刑后2001年以来，越南股票激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/vietnam-stocks-surge-most-since-2001-after-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）暂停了他的大部分互惠关税之后，越南的股票飙升，这加剧了乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/vietnam-stocks-surge-most-since-2001-after-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 02:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库的摇摆触发全球债券市场余震</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国国债市场混乱的日子之后，从澳大利亚到日本的债券浪费了，迫使交易者面对贸易战的波动刚刚开始的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/treasuries-chaos-is-triggering-aftershocks-across-global-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者押注刺激</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/chinese-shares-climb-for-third-day-as-investors-bet-on-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股票上涨了第三天，反映了投资者对北京提供更多刺激支持的期望，并希望与美国达成贸易协定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/chinese-shares-climb-for-third-day-as-investors-bet-on-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战构成新的风险，中国的消费者通货紧缩持续存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/china-s-consumer-deflation-persists-as-trade-war-poses-new-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与美国的一场贸易战升级，中国的消费者通货膨胀率在3月的第二个月延长了，威胁要对价格更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/china-s-consumer-deflation-persists-as-trade-war-poses-new-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国关税缓刑后，台湾库存量规飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/taiwan-stock-gauge-surges-by-record-after-us-tariff-reprieve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾的股票在周四的记录中飙升，在唐纳德·特朗普总统宣布对大多数贸易伙伴的互惠职责持续90天之后，追踪了全球篮板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/taiwan-stock-gauge-surges-by-record-after-us-tariff-reprieve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 01:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>七＆amp;我在一个月内回购，市场反弹大多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/seven-i-jumps-most-in-month-on-buyback-plan-broader-buying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[七＆amp; I Holdings Co.在宣布一项计划在明年的6000亿日元（40亿美元）股票的计划中，在一个月内提高了最大的收益，这有助于减轻投资者对较弱的收益前景的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/seven-i-jumps-most-in-month-on-buyback-plan-broader-buying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 00:37:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于贸易战的市场担忧持续存在，石油恢复损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当投资者努力解决美国关税政策的突然转变时，石油扩大了一场动荡的奔跑，在唐纳德·特朗普总统决定停止一些征税的决定之后，期货恢复了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 23:25:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股票加入全球拉力赛，国库会收益：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）暂停了他大部分盛大的互惠关税之后，全球金融市场反弹，亚洲股票在两年多以来都发行了他们的增长。在动荡的会议之后，国库会集会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 22:44:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
